Now I'm setting up the test project structure with net10.0 targeting, EF Core InMemory provider, MSTest, and Moq for mocking. I need to be careful with the static notification queue—draining it between tests—and handle the TPH inheritance model properly in SchoolContext. The RowVersion column also needs consideration for concurrency testing.

